data.description: REFRIGERATOR, WASHER AND DRYER CONVEY WITH THE HOUSE! Great three bed, two bath with lots of parking in a quiet neighborhood! A large living room welcomes you as you walk in the front door, but not before walking through the home's courtyard. The living room leads to the updated kitchen and spacious dining room. The master bedroom has an ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. A full bathroom at the end of the hallway sits between the two other bedrooms. Off the dining room is a closed in back patio overlooking the HUGE back yard with mature trees and shed on the side of the home. There is ample parking with a two car garage and an attached carport. Within minutes of lots of shopping and a large variety of restaurants as well.
